{"about_the_game":"In The Steps as we know them, you use the moves of chess to find your way through different worlds. It is a puzzle game with a relaxing atmosphere. The game has simple mechanics, but is challenging at the same time.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573800/extras/Horsemove.gif?t=1622484625\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Different situations</h2><br>Every world you come across uses a different chess piece and brings a different tactic with it. The levels build up from the easy moves of a pawn to the difficult situations of a knight. Sometimes you can work your way through by being stubborn. In other levels you have to take a step back and take a second look.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573800/extras/ScreenTower.png?t=1622484625\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The game</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 worlds<br></li><li>6 different chess pieces<br></li><li>~7 levels per world<br></li><li>From easy to complicated</li></ul><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573800/extras/Towermove.gif?t=1622484625\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Step by step","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1573800/dd63bd46fb8c9af60a7c3ab289f1427bc17770a3.jpg"},{"name":"Frozone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1573800/3aeb299ea7bfe06da7c9835123de6b5ab2b8d9b2.jpg"},{"name":"Viva la vida","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1573800/cce4c5d986ffd16ce530994f791785610283da2d.jpg"},{"name":"Rise of the Queen","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1573800/0b952db8b1229c9dc121ba3e91900290f8befbd3.jpg"},{"name":"It's all about perspective","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1573